<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-width: 100%;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #222222;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Activate Your Account</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us! Please use the following OTP to activate your account:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= year %> E-Shop. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
